										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = aeo
											value = 0.001
										}
									}
								}
							}
							set_variable = {

								value = 0
							}
						}

							divide_variable = {

								which = aax
							}
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								OR = {

											which = aay
											value = 0
										}
									}
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = aec

										}
									}
								}

								which = aec
								value = 0
							}

						else = {

								which = aec
								which = aay

						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = axq
							which = aen
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = axr
							which = aeo
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = axs
							which = aec
						}
						multiply_variable = { 
							which = axq
							value = 100
						}
						multiply_variable = { 
							which = axr
							value = 100
						}
						multiply_variable = { 
							which = axs
							value = 100
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ayo
							which = awy
						}
						change_variable = { 
							which = ayo
							which = awz
						}
						change_variable = { 
							which = ayo
							which = axa
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ayu
							which = ayo

						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = {

										value = 0.001

											value = 0

						else = { 
							divide_variable = { 
								which = aep
								which = aaw

						if = { 
							limit = { 
								OR = { 
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = aax
											value = 0
										}
									}
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = aeq
											value = 0.001
										}
									}
								}
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = aeq
								value = 0
							}
						}
						else = { 
							divide_variable = { 
								which = aeq
								which = aax
							}
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								OR = { 
									AND = {

											which = aay
											value = 0
										}
									}
									AND = {

										}
									}

							which = axu
							which = aeq

							value = 100
						}
					}
					else_if = {

							AND = { 
								is_variable_equal = { 
									which = adx
									value = 4
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = baa
							value = 100
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								is_variable_equal = {

									value = 4
								}
							}
						}

					}
					else_if = {

								}
							}
						}

							value = 100
						}
					}

							AND = {

									value = 4
								}
							}
						}

									value = 4
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = {

			}
		}
	}

country_event = { 
	id = DG_Hussites.002
	title = "DG_Hussites.002.title"
	desc = "DG_Hussites.002.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	trigger = { 
		NOT = { 
			has_country_flag = hussite_presence
		}
	}
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = "DG_Hussites.002.opta"
		trigger = { 
			ai = no
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_country_flag = hus_spread_info
			set_country_flag = hus_inquis_info
			set_country_flag = hus_convert_info
			set_country_flag = hus_unrest_info
			set_country_flag = hus_end_info
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "DG_Hussites.002.optb"
		trigger = { 
			ai = no
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			clr_country_flag = hus_spread_info
			clr_country_flag = hus_inquis_info
			clr_country_flag = hus_convert_info
			clr_country_flag = hus_unrest_info
			clr_country_flag = hus_end_info
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "DG_Hussites.002.optc"
		trigger = { 
			ai = no
		}
		country_event = { 
			id = DG_Notification.041
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "EVT_AI"
		trigger = { 
			ai = yes
		}
	}
	after = { 
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_presence
				}
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				set_country_flag = hussite_presence
			}
		}
	}
}

country_event = { 
	id = DG_Hussites.006
	title = "DG_Hussites.006.title"
	desc = "DG_Hussites.006.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = "DG_Hussites.006.opta"
		trigger = { 
			is_emperor = no
		}
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 25
		}
		custom_tooltip = hussite_25
		random_country = { 
			limit = { 
				is_emperor = yes
			}
			reverse_add_opinion = { 
				who = ROOT
				modifier = dg_broken_promises
			}
		}
		add_opinion = { 
			who = PAP
			modifier = papacy_bad
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			every_owned_province = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = asx
							value = 0.001
						}
					}
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = ata
					value = -20
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = atb
					value = -20
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = ata
								value = 100.001
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 100
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ata
									value = 0
								}
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 0
					}
				}
				set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = POP_CLLoyProv_-20
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_country_flag = support_04
			clr_country_flag = accept_04
			clr_country_flag = silence_04
			every_owned_province = { 
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							AND = { 
								is_variable_equal = { 
									which = adv
									value = 4
								}
							}
							AND = { 
								is_variable_equal = { 
									which = adx
									value = 4
								}
							}
							AND = { 
								is_variable_equal = { 
									which = adz
									value = 4
								}
							}
							AND = { 
								is_variable_equal = { 
									which = aeb

						}
					}

								value = 4
							}
						}
					}
				}
				add_unrest = 5
			}
			add_ruler_modifier = { 
				name = "leaning_catholic"
				hidden = yes
			}
		}
	}

				}
				remove_country_modifier = dg_rc_10
				remove_country_modifier = dg_rc_20
				remove_country_modifier = dg_rc_30
				remove_country_modifier = dg_rc_40
				remove_country_modifier = dg_rc_50
				remove_country_modifier = dg_rc_70
				remove_country_modifier = dg_rc_80
				remove_country_modifier = dg_rc_90
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = opw
							value = 50
						}
					}
				}
				add_country_modifier = { 
					name = dg_rc_50
					duration = -1
					hidden = yes
				}
				remove_country_modifier = dg_rc_10
				remove_country_modifier = dg_rc_20

				remove_country_modifier = dg_rc_70
				remove_country_modifier = dg_rc_80
				remove_country_modifier = dg_rc_90

			else_if = {

							value = 40
						}
					}

country_event = { 
	id = DG_Hussites.010
	title = "DG_Hussites.010.title"
	desc = "DG_Hussites.010.desc"
	picture = protestant_defenestration
	fire_only_once = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes
	major = yes
	trigger = { 
		has_country_flag = hussite_league_formed
		OR = { 
			has_country_flag = accept_04
			has_country_flag = silence_04
		}
		capital_scope = { 
			has_owner_culture = yes
			OR = { 
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = adv
						value = 4
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = adx
						value = 4
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = adz
						value = 4
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = aeb
						value = 4
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = aed
						value = 4
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = aef
						value = 4
					}
				}
			}
		}
		NOT = { 
			has_global_flag = hussite_wars
		}
		NOT = { 
			religion = hussite
		}
		NOT = { 
			is_religion_enabled = protestant
		}
	}
	immediate = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_global_flag = hussite_wars
			set_country_flag = hussite_wars_target
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = accept_04
				}
				clr_country_flag = accept_04
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = silence_04
				}
				clr_country_flag = silence_04
			}
			every_known_country = { 
				limit = { 
					religion = catholic
					OR = { 
						is_elector = yes
						is_emperor = yes
						is_papal_controller = yes
						is_neighbor_of = ROOT
						is_subject_of = ROOT
					}
				}
				add_opinion = { 
					who = ROOT
					modifier = throneless_king
				}
			}
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_heir = yes
					is_lesser_in_union = no
				}
				exile_heir_as = hussite_war_heir
				set_country_flag = hussite_war_heir
			}
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_war_heir
				}
				any_known_country = { 
					dynasty = ROOT
					government = monarchy
					has_regency = no
					is_female = no
					num_of_cities = 8
					AND = { 
						OR = { 
							is_subject = no
							is_subject_of_type = tributary_state
							is_subject_of_type = close_tributary_state
						}
					}
				}
			}
			random_known_country = { 
				limit = { 
					dynasty = ROOT
					government = monarchy
					has_regency = no
					is_female = no
					num_of_cities = 8
					AND = { 
						OR = { 
							is_subject = no
							is_subject_of_type = tributary_state
							is_subject_of_type = close_tributary_state
						}
					}
				}
				set_country_flag = hussite_war_heir_2
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_war_heir
				}
				any_known_country = { 
					marriage_with = ROOT
					government = monarchy
					has_regency = no
					is_female = no
					num_of_cities = 8
					AND = { 
						OR = { 
							is_subject = no
							is_subject_of_type = tributary_state
							is_subject_of_type = close_tributary_state
						}
					}
				}
			}
			random_known_country = { 
				limit = { 
					marriage_with = ROOT
					government = monarchy
					has_regency = no
					is_female = no
					num_of_cities = 8
					AND = { 
						OR = { 
							is_subject = no
							is_subject_of_type = tributary_state
							is_subject_of_type = close_tributary_state
						}
					}
				}
				set_country_flag = hussite_war_heir_3
			}
		}
		define_ruler = { 
			name = "Interregnum"
			regency = yes
			claim = 50
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				primary_culture = czech
			}
			define_heir = { 
				name = "Jiri"
				dynasty = "Podebrad"
				age = 0
				adm = 5
				dip = 4
				mil = 3
				claim = 25
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "DG_Hussites.010.opta"
		hidden_effect = { 
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						stability = -2
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = ahf
					value = 0
				}
			}
			else = { 
				add_stability = -2
			}
		}
		tooltip = { 
			add_stability = -2
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				is_emperor_of_china = yes
			}
			add_mandate = -10
		}
		capital_scope = { 
			spawn_rebels = { 
				type = hussite_rebels
				size = 4
				win = yes
				leader = "Jan Zelivsky"
			}
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = heretic_bastion
				duration = 1095
			}
			set_province_flag = hussite_bastion
		}
		random_owned_province = { 
			limit = { 
				has_owner_culture = yes
				is_capital = no
				OR = { 
					AND = { 
						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = adv
							value = 4
						}
					}
					AND = { 
						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = adx
							value = 4
						}
					}
					AND = { 
						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = adz
							value = 4
						}
					}
					AND = { 
						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = aeb
							value = 4
						}
					}
					AND = { 
						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = aed
							value = 4
						}
					}
					AND = { 
						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = aef
							value = 4
						}
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = aax
						value = 5
					}
				}
			}
			spawn_rebels = { 
				type = hussite_rebels
				size = 3
				win = yes
			}
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = heretic_bastion
				duration = 1095
			}
		}
	}
}

country_event = { 
	id = DG_Hussites.012
	title = DG_Hussites.012.title
	desc = DG_Hussites.012.desc
	picture = hussite_barons
	fire_only_once = yes
	major = yes
	trigger = { 
		has_country_flag = hussite_league_formed
		OR = { 
			AND = { 
				has_country_flag = hussite_wars_target
				has_spawned_rebels = hussite_rebels
				NOT = { 
					religion = hussite
				}
				any_owned_province = { 
					has_province_flag = hussite_bastion
					OR = { 
						AND = { 
							is_variable_equal = { 
								which = adv
								value = 4
							}
						}
						AND = { 
							is_variable_equal = { 
								which = adx
								value = 4
							}
						}
						AND = { 
							is_variable_equal = { 
								which = adz
								value = 4
							}
						}
						AND = { 
							is_variable_equal = { 
								which = aeb
								value = 4
							}
						}
						AND = { 
							is_variable_equal = { 
								which = aed
								value = 4
							}
						}
						AND = { 
							is_variable_equal = { 
								which = aef
								value = 4
							}
						}
					}
					controlled_by = REB
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				has_country_flag = hussite_league_formed
				has_country_flag = support_04
			}
			religion = hussite
		}
		NOT = { 
			is_religion_enabled = protestant
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		months = 24
		modifier = { 
			religion = hussite
			factor = 0.5
		}
	}
	immediate = { 
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					religion = hussite
				}
			}
			change_religion = hussite
			force_converted = yes
			hidden_effect = { 
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = {

					}

									value = 100.001
								}
							}
						}

							value = 100
						}
					}

										value = 0
									}
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = asq
							value = 0
						}
					}
					set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
				}
			}

			hidden_effect = {

							}
						}
					}

		NOT = { 
			has_country_flag = hussite_crown
		}

	}

				}

			}
			modifier = {

					has_country_flag = hussite_crown_candidate
					is_rival = ROOT

			}
			modifier = { 
				any_known_country = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_crown_candidate
					is_enemy = ROOT
				}
				factor = 0.7
			}
		}

country_event = { 
	id = DG_Hussites.018
	title = DG_Hussites.018.title
	desc = DG_Hussites.018.desc
	picture = catholic_court
	fire_only_once = yes
	major = yes
	trigger = { 
		has_country_flag = hussite_wars_target
		religion = hussite
		has_regency = no
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		months = 6
	}
	immediate = { 
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_crown
				}
			}
			set_country_flag = hussite_crown
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Hussites.018.opta
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_spawned_rebels = hussite_rebels
			}
			disband_rebels = hussite_rebels
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_spawned_rebels = catholic_rebels
			}
			disband_rebels = catholic_rebels
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			change_variable = { 
				which = ahf
				value = 600
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = ahf
							value = 1200
						}
					}
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						stability = 3
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 1200
					}
				}
				else = { 
					subtract_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 1200
					}
					add_stability = 1
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = ahf
								value = 0
							}
						}
					}
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							stability = -2
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 0
					}
				}
				else = { 
					change_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 1200
					}
					add_stability = -1
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				which = ahf
			}
			divide_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				value = 12
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				value = 0.1
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				value = 10
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = lsc
				value = 100
			}
			subtract_variable = { 
				which = lsc
				which = ahd
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = POP_StabAdd50
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				is_emperor_of_china = yes
			}
			add_mandate = 2.5
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			every_owned_province = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = asn
							value = 0.001
						}
					}
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = asq
					value = 10
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = asr
					value = 10
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = asq
								value = 100.001
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = asq
						value = 100
					}
				}
				else_if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = asq
									value = 0
								}
							}
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = asq
						value = 0
					}
				}
				set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = POP_NOLoyProv_10
		hidden_effect = { 
			every_owned_province = {

							which = ass

						}
					}
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = asv
					value = 10
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = asw
					value = 10
				}
				if = {

						value = 1200
					}
				}
				else = { 
					subtract_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 1200
					}
					add_stability = 1
				}
			}
			else_if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = ahf
								value = 0
							}
						}
					}
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							stability = -2
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 0
					}
				}
				else = { 
					change_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 1200
					}
					add_stability = -1
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				which = ahf
			}
			divide_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				value = 12
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				value = 0.1
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = ahd
				value = 10
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = lsc
				value = 100
			}
			subtract_variable = { 
				which = lsc
				which = ahd
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = POP_StabSubtract50
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				is_emperor_of_china = yes
			}
			add_mandate = -2.5
		}
		random_owned_province = { 
			limit = { 
				is_capital = no
				religion = catholic
			}
			spawn_rebels = { 
				type = catholic_rebels
				size = 3
				leader = "Puta z Castolovic"
				win = yes
				should_take_capital = yes
			}
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = heretic_bastion
				duration = 1095
			}
		}
	}
}

			}

					}

					}

country_event = { 
	id = DG_Hussites.025
	title = DG_Hussites.025.title
	desc = DG_Hussites.025.desc
	picture = catholic_heresy
	trigger = { 
		is_papal_controller = yes
		PAP = { 
			has_regency = no
		}
		any_known_country = { 
			has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
			has_country_modifier = edict_of_tolerance
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		years = 10
		modifier = { 
			any_known_country = { 
				has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
				NOT = { 
					religion = catholic
				}
			}
			factor = 0.1
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Hussites.025.opta
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 25
			modifier = { 
				any_known_country = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
					NOT = { 
						religion = catholic
					}
				}
				factor = 0
			}
			modifier = { 
				any_known_country = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
					alliance_with = ROOT
				}
				factor = 1.4
			}
			modifier = { 
				any_known_country = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
					marriage_with = ROOT
				}
				factor = 1.4
			}
			modifier = { 
				any_known_country = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
					is_subject_of = ROOT
				}
				factor = 1.4
			}
			modifier = { 
				any_known_country = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
					alliance_with = PAP
				}
				factor = 2
			}
			modifier = { 
				any_known_country = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
					truce_with = ROOT
				}
				factor = 0.7
			}
			modifier = { 
				any_known_country = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
					is_rival = ROOT
				}
				factor = 0.7
			}
			modifier = { 
				any_known_country = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
					is_enemy = ROOT
				}
				factor = 0.5
			}
			modifier = { 
				any_known_country = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
					war_with = ROOT
				}
				factor = 0.5
			}
		}
		random_country = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
			}
			add_opinion = { 
				who = ROOT
				modifier = papacy_great
			}
			add_opinion = { 
				who = PAP
				modifier = papacy_great
			}
		}
		add_papal_influence = -5
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Hussites.025.optb
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 75
			modifier = { 
				has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
				factor = 0
			}
		}
		random_country = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_flag = hussite_compacta
			}
			add_opinion = { 
				who = ROOT
				modifier = papacy_bad
			}
			add_opinion = { 
				who = PAP
				modifier = papacy_bad
			}
			country_event = { 
				id = DG_Hussites.026
				days = 30
			}
			clr_country_flag = hussite_compacta
		}
		add_reform_desire = 0.001
	}

country_event = { 
	id = DG_Hussites.026
	title = DG_Hussites.026.title
	desc = DG_Hussites.026.desc
	picture = catholic_heresy
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = DG_Hussites.026.opta
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 40
		}
		reverse_add_opinion = { 
			who = PAP
			modifier = disobeyed_religious_leader
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				religion = catholic
			}
			add_legitimacy = -10
			add_papal_influence = -20
			hidden_effect = { 
				every_owned_province = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = asx
								value = 0.001
							}
						}
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = -20
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = atb
						value = -20
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ata
									value = 100.001
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 100
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							NOT = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = ata
										value = 0
									}
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 0
						}
					}
					set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
				}
			}
			custom_tooltip = POP_CLLoyProv_-20
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = DG_Hussites.026.optb
		ai_chance = { 
			factor = 60
			modifier = { 
				NOT = { 
					religion = catholic
				}
				factor = 0
			}
			modifier = { 
				dominant_religion = hussite
				factor = 0.1
			}
			modifier = { 
				NOT = { 
					stability = 0
				}
				factor = 0.7
			}
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				religion = catholic
			}
			add_legitimacy = 5
			add_papal_influence = 10
			hidden_effect = { 
				every_owned_province = { 
					limit = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = asx
								value = 0.001
							}
						}
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = ata
						value = 10
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = atb
						value = 10
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								check_variable = { 
									which = ata
									value = 100.001
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 100
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							NOT = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = ata
										value = 0
									}
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = ata
							value = 0
						}
					}
					set_province_flag = Unrest_Update
				}
			}
			custom_tooltip = POP_CLLoyProv_10
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_country_modifier = edict_of_tolerance
			}
			remove_country_modifier = edict_of_tolerance
			hidden_effect = { 
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							stability = -2
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ahf
						value = 0
					}
				}
				else = { 
					add_stability = -1
				}
			}
			tooltip = { 
				add_stability = -1
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					is_emperor_of_china = yes
				}
				add_mandate = -5
			}
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				any_owned_province = { 
					religion = hussite
				}
			}
			every_owned_province = { 
				limit = { 
					religion = hussite
				}
				add_unrest = 10
			}
		}
	}
}

country_event = { 
	id = DG_Hussites.100
	title = "DG_Hussites.100.title"
	desc = "DG_Hussites.100.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	hidden = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				NOT = { 
					has_country_flag = hussite_presence
				}
			}
			country_event = { 
				id = DG_Hussites.101
			}
			set_country_flag = hussite_presence
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				had_country_flag = { 
					flag = hussite_presence
					days = 36500
				}
			}
			random_list = { 
				1 = { 
					country_event = { 
						id = DG_Hussites.101
					}
				}
				99 = { }
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				had_country_flag = { 
					flag = hussite_presence
					days = 27375
				}
			}
			random_list = { 
				5 = { 
					country_event = { 
						id = DG_Hussites.101
					}
				}
				95 = { }
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				had_country_flag = { 
					flag = hussite_presence
					days = 21900
				}
			}
			random_list = { 
				15 = { 
					country_event = { 
						id = DG_Hussites.101
					}
				}
				85 = { }
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				had_country_flag = { 
					flag = hussite_presence
					days = 18250
				}
			}
			random_list = { 
				30 = { 
					country_event = { 
						id = DG_Hussites.101
					}
				}
				70 = { }
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				had_country_flag = { 
					flag = hussite_presence
					days = 14600
				}
			}
			random_list = { 
				40 = { 
					country_event = { 
						id = DG_Hussites.101
					}
				}
				60 = { }
			}
		}
		else_if = { 
			limit = { 
				had_country_flag = { 
					flag = hussite_presence
					days = 7300
				}
			}
			random_list = { 
				55 = { 
					country_event = { 
						id = DG_Hussites.101
					}
				}
				45 = { }
			}
		}
		else = { 
			random_list = { 
				70 = { 
					country_event = { 
						id = DG_Hussites.101
					}
				}
				30 = { }
			}
		}
	}

						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = aes
							which = axf
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = aeg
							which = axg
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								OR = { 
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = aaw
											value = 0
										}
									}
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = aer
											value = 0.001
										}
									}
								}
							}
							set_variable = { 
								which = aer
								value = 0
							}
						}
						else = { 
							divide_variable = { 
								which = aer
								which = aaw
							}

						if = { 
							limit = { 
								OR = { 
									AND = { 
										is_variable_equal = { 
											which = aax

									}

							which = aer

							which = aes

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Hussites.111
	title = "DG_Hussites.111.title"
	desc = "DG_Hussites.111.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	hidden = yes
	trigger = { 
		always = no
		is_religion_enabled = hussite
		owner = { 
			NOT = { 
				religion = hussite
			}
		}
		OR = { 
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = adv
					value = 4
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = adx
					value = 4
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = adz
					value = 4
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = aeb
					value = 4
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = aed
					value = 4
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = aef
					value = 4
				}
			}
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		years = 5
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.90
			OR = { 
				AND = {

					}
				}
				AND = { 
					AND = { 
						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = aeb
							value = 4
						}
					}

						}
					}
				}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Hussites.118
	title = "DG_Hussites.118.title"
	desc = "DG_Hussites.118.desc"
	picture = ANGLICAN_SERMON_eventPicture
	trigger = { 
		has_province_flag = printing_press_p
		NOT = { 
			religion_years = { 
				hussite = 50
			}
		}
		AND = { 
			continent = europe
			religion = hussite
			NOT = { 
				province_id = 2530
			}
			is_reformation_center = no
			is_island = no
			expelling_minorities = no
			development = 10
			NOT = { 
				Academia = 100
			}
			NOT = { 
				current_age = age_of_revolutions
			}
			NOT = { 
				calc_true_if = { 
					all_province = { 
						continent = europe
						religion = ROOT
						is_reformation_center = yes
					}
					amount = 3
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				any_neighbor_province = { 
					is_reformation_center = yes
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				any_province = { 
					superregion = PREV
					is_reformation_center = yes
					religion = hussite
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_climate = tropical
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_climate = arid
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_climate = arctic
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_terrain = arctic
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_terrain = taiga
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_terrain = tundra
			}
		}
		owner = { 
			religion = hussite
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		years = 5
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.8
			owner = { 
				tag = BOH
			}
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.5
			has_province_flag = hus_craddle
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.5
			province_id = 268
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 5.0
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = accept_04
			}
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 10.0
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = silence_04
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.GOOD"
		trigger = { 
			owner = { 
				religion = hussite
			}
		}
		add_reform_center = hussite
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_province_modifier = religious_enthusiasm
			}
			extend_province_modifier = { 
				name = religious_enthusiasm
				duration = 3650
			}
		}
		else = { 
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = religious_enthusiasm
				duration = 3650
				hidden = yes
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.DAMN"
		trigger = { 
			owner = { 
				NOT = { 
					religion = hussite
				}
			}
		}
		add_reform_center = hussite
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_province_modifier = heretic_centre
			}
			extend_province_modifier = { 
				name = heretic_centre
				duration = 3650
			}
		}
		else = { 
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = heretic_centre
				duration = 3650
				hidden = yes
			}
		}
	}
}

								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn
								value = 0.5
							}
							add_devastation = 0.5
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = amn
										value = 0.25
									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn
								value = 0.25
							}
							add_devastation = 0.25
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = amn
										value = 0.1
									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn
								value = 0.1
							}
							add_devastation = 0.1
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = amn
							value = 0
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = kdt
							value = 0
						}
					}
					else_if = { 
						limit = { 
							AND = { 
								is_variable_equal = { 
									which = aef
									value = 4
								}
							}
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = kdt
							which = ayw
						}
						multiply_variable = { 
							which = kdt
							value = 0.90
						}
						divide_variable = { 
							which = kdt
							value = 10
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = amn
							which = kdt
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = amn
										value = 64
									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn
								value = 64
							}
							add_devastation = 64
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = amn
										value = 32
									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn
								value = 32
							}
							add_devastation = 32
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = amn
										value = 16
									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn
								value = 16
							}
							add_devastation = 16
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = amn
										value = 8
									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn
								value = 8
							}
							add_devastation = 8
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = amn
										value = 4
									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn
								value = 4
							}
							add_devastation = 4
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = amn
										value = 2
									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn
								value = 2
							}
							add_devastation = 2
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = amn
										value = 1
									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn
								value = 1
							}
							add_devastation = 1
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = amn
										value = 0.5
									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn
								value = 0.5
							}
							add_devastation = 0.5
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = amn
										value = 0.25
									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn
								value = 0.25
							}
							add_devastation = 0.25
						}
						if = { 
							limit = { 
								AND = { 
									check_variable = { 
										which = amn
										value = 0.1
									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn
								value = 0.1
							}
							add_devastation = 0.1
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = amn
							value = 0
						}
						set_variable = { 
							which = kdt
							value = 0
						}
					}
					if = { 
						limit = { 
							owner = { 
								has_country_flag = hus_unrest_info
							}
						}
						set_province_flag = mn_trauma_90
					}
				}
			}
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				owner = { 
					has_country_flag = hus_unrest_info
				}
			}
			province_event = { 
				id = DG_Hussites.302
			}
		}
	}
}
province_event = { 
	id = DG_Hussites.302
	title = "DG_Hussites.301.title"
	desc = "DG_Hussites.301.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.OHNO"
		trigger_switch = { 
			on_trigger = has_province_flag
			mn_trauma_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_10_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_20 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_20_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_30 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_30_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_40 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_40_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_50 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_50_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_60 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_60_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_70 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_70_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_80 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_80_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_90 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_90_tt
			}
		}
	}
	after = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_20
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_30
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_40
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_50
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_60
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_70
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_80
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_90
		}
	}
}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Hussites.312
	title = "DG_Hussites.311.title"
	desc = "DG_Hussites.311.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.OHNO"
		trigger_switch = { 
			on_trigger = has_province_flag
			mn_unrest_min_1 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_min_1_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_min_5 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_min_2_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_min_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_min_3_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_low_1 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_low_1_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_low_5 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_low_2_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_low_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_low_3_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_mid_1 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_mid_1_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_mid_5 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_mid_2_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_mid_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_mid_3_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_imp_1 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_imp_1_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_imp_5 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_imp_2_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_imp_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_imp_3_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_max_1 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_max_1_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_max_5 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_max_2_tt
			}
			mn_unrest_max_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_unrest_max_3_tt
			}
		}
	}
	after = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_min_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_min_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_min_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_low_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_low_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_low_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_mid_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_mid_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_mid_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_imp_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_imp_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_imp_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_max_1
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_max_5
			clr_province_flag = mn_unrest_max_10
		}
	}
}
province_event = { 
	id = DG_Hussites.901
	title = "DG_Hussites.901.title"
	desc = "DG_Hussites.901.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	hidden = yes
	trigger = { 
		is_religion_enabled = protestant
		OR = { 
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = adv
					value = 4
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = adx
					value = 4
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = adz
					value = 4
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = aeb
					value = 4
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = aed
					value = 4
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = aef
					value = 4
				}
			}
		}
		NOT = { 
			owner = { 
				religion = hussite
			}
		}
		OR = { 
			owner = { 
				religion = protestant
			}
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = support_02
			}
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = accept_02
			}
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		months = 300
		modifier = { 
			factor = 10
			owner = { 
				religion = hussite
				stability = 3
			}
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 2
			owner = { 
				religion = hussite
				stability = -1
			}
		}

			factor = 0.75

				religion = protestant

					NOT = {

							}

				}

							which = adv
							value = 4
						}
					}
				}

						}

								}

							value = 0
						}

							which = aeh
							value = 0
						}
					}

							which = aeh
							which = aaw
